Name: Celestial_a04
Description: REQUIRES CD2_beta_12b, MEVv5_4 AND DEA_a05t2. Celestial, shortened as CS, is a spin off of ND and the dial-down version of Interstellar with some interesting twists on modded enemies. a04: Nitra Multiplier on Sabotage Mission type is increased (1 Complexity x1.2 -> x1.3, 2 Complexity x1 -> x1.1). The Sun and The Moon DifficultyRating 175 -> 150, they bleed out even more faster in 1p setting (dies in 10s after 30s time pass). Ninja DifficultyRating 75 -> 50, Min and Max SpawnCount is now buffed and scaled to player count, at 4p it is at 3 and 4 Min/Max SpawnCount respectively. Plague Bomber DifficultyRating 175 -> 110. Increase NoSpawnWithin for dangerous type enemies (Bulk type enemies). Ice Bulk HP is back to normal (previously it has x0.75 HP), Ice Bulk MaxSpawnCount 0 -> 1. Barrier Spitter DifficultyRating 80 -> 60. Vomit Spitter DifficultyRating 40 -> 35, MaxSpawnCount 19 -> 45, their base - Shooter_Ground, is now replaced to be Shooter_Bouncer, so they have slightly faster projectile speed, lower shooting arc and doesn't stuck the projectile on the ceiling anymore (mostly). Glacial Praetorian MaxSpawnCount 2 -> 1. Sniper Turret from Sabotage Mission DifficultyRating 12 -> 36.
